        "Description": "(6 months later)\r47, I finally got a lead. Turns out that Zana Kazem was an employer for Providence, he was finding new Herald&apos;s. His last mail was to Dino Bosco, a big time actor. He wrote that the next meeting of Providence will be in the same place as always, we need to know where these meeting are being held. Go to Sapienza, Dino is there filming his new movie, capture him and get the information about the meeting place, kill him after. We need that information now, so be quick 47.",
